content: Such matters involve risks and uncertainties that may cause actual results to differ materially include, but are not limited to, the Company's acceptance and the Company's products in the market, success in obtaining new customers, success in product development, ability to execute the business model and strategic plans, success in integrating acquired entities and assets, ability to obtain capital, ability to continue its going concern and all of the risks and related information described from time to time in the Company's filings with the Securities and Exchange Commission, including the financial statements and related information pertaining to the Company's annual report on Form 10-K for the year ended December 31, 2022, filed with the Securities and Exchange Commission.
